summary: I miss London and my best friend. I miss dressing like the 1989's Taylor. I miss dancing and jumping in a sparkly skirt with the...
body: I miss London and my best friend. I miss dressing like the 1989’s Taylor. I miss dancing and jumping in a sparkly skirt with the biggest smile ever. I miss the tears in my eyes listening live ‘Fifteen’. I miss the confetti and the lights and getting shocked by Robbie Williams as a surprise guest (that was so crazy). And I miss the whole experience, the people, the B stages SO close, Taylor joking and my best friend just besides me. And oh my god how I miss @taylorswift .
